                    <div class="w3-container w3-light-grey">
                        <p>Next week we'll start a 2 week off-season before Season 7. We'd like to note that the indicated relagation/promotion slots are dependant on inactive drivers & influx of new drivers as well! final tiers will be announced before the season starts.</p>
                        <p>Here's what you need to do before next season starts:</p>

                        <p><strong>Current drivers</strong></p>
                        <p>Fill this form and that's all. Just keep up with the news and complete this season to secure
                            a spot on next season. https://forms.gle/ygLXZJHcDXEuNb7k9</p>
                        <br>
                        <p><strong>New drivers</strong></p>
                        <p>Fill the new version of Driver profile. This will cover everything. Before the season there
                            will be bigger placements organized but you can join the current placements to get placed
                            into a tier for the last couple rounds. https://forms.gle/PL8Do6qA7K3FpjSH9</p>

