                        <p><strong>JRC Live RX edition</strong></p>
                        <p>When the main league goes into a 2 week break period, JRC Live will return once more. This time an rx event will be held in addition to the showdown event between the top drivers. Check #jrc-live for signups & info</p>


                        <p><strong>Side Series</strong></p>
                        <p>JRC Historic & Themed will head into new seasons at the start of the off-season. If you thought the group B cars were a pain to handle, you're in for a surprise as RGT graces us with it's presence in the new themed season.</p>
                        <p>New kid on the block the JRC Endurance Series will start alongside them. This one will see you fighting for survival, rather than outright speed.
                            Given the extreme nature of the routes this series will follow a two weekly calendar. To celebrate the inaugural season all points-scoring competitors will have a chance to win a steam game at the end.</p>
                        
